snippet.title: Black Hole for the Commodore VIC-20 / Commodore VC-20
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

Black Hole is an action game, with a star-shaped black hole in the middle that tries to suck you in.

Try to avoid being sucked in and shoot asteroids for points.
